Java Developers Conference 2013

For the fifth year, Java professionals and students will gather next March (on the 8th & 9th of March) in Cairo for the biggest Java conference in the Middle East and Africa (Java Developers Conference 2013), with more than 40 exciting sessions, And speakers from Egypt and around the world to share their experience with you.

Don't miss the chance to be up to date with latest technologies!

Register Now !
